EXTRACTED VALUE: Even at the reduced $49.99 price point Facebreaker must be avoided unless you like no-brainer button mashing boxing.
Edward Carnby's return had the potential to be the next Silent Hill. What we ended up with is more reminiscent of Trespasser.
Both shallow and a waste of a good property.
The only knock on Bullet Witch is that the graphics are a bit choppy in some areas.
